OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming less frequent for a time into
OL,7,Fthe evening, before returning later in
OL,8,Fthe night, perhaps merging to give
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain later in the
OL,10,Fnight. Feeling cool, and turning
OL,11,Fchilly in rural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FShowery rain breaking up
OL,14,Fthrough the morning, then sunshine and
OL,15,Fshowers with the risk of hail and
OL,16,Fthunder in the north, before these
OL,17,Ffade towards evening. Winds lighter
OL,18,Fthan Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
